## File Structure

```
src/
├── components/<feature>/   One directory per feature domain
│   └── ComponentName.tsx   PascalCase, named export
├── hooks/
│   └── useHookName.ts      camelCase, always prefixed with "use"
├── utils/
│   └── utilName.ts         camelCase, pure functions only
├── module_bindings/        ← GENERATED — never edit manually
│                             Regenerate: npm run spacetime:generate
├── App.tsx                 Layout shell + connecting state
├── App.css                 All component styles (co-located by class name)
├── index.css               Design tokens, global resets, typography
└── main.tsx                SpacetimeDBProvider + React root
```

When adding a new feature:
- New shared state → new table in `spacetimedb/src/schema.ts`
- New mutation → new reducer in `spacetimedb/src/index.ts`
- New UI component → `src/components/<feature>/ComponentName.tsx`
- New logic hook → `src/hooks/useHookName.ts`
- New pure utility → `src/utils/utilName.ts`

